{"tid":643887,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【鏟草男女】拯救獌聯的「曼狗」","createTime":"2018-04-26T22:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T02:33:45.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f14ba34ec90e3821dd7afd42c76696a04872c3c9","tid":643887,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T22:57:46.000Z","msg":"13小時前  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=WQrSQgn5tsVCbU%2B96v3TfhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=1a58a311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】在香港，有些球迷會以「狗」來稱敵對球迷，例如叫曼聯球迷做「曼狗」，後來索性將「狗」與球會名融合，變成「獌」，尚有「猁」及「軌」。透過今日這篇文章，筆者想介紹一隻曼狗，是貨真價實的曼狗，如果沒有這隻狗，可能現在根本沒有曼聯。在百多年前，一隻狗拯救了破產邊緣的曼聯。<br />\n撰文：洛輝<br />\n<br />\n20世紀初，中國仍然是滿清時，曼聯還未叫曼聯，而是Newton Heath。那段日子，Newton Heath的財政問題愈來愈嚴重，負債愈來愈多，到1901年，升至超過2500鎊。為了挽救球會，球員都要在市集拋頭露面，向大眾籌款，包括隊長史特福特（Harry Stafford）帶住籌款箱，走遍曼市街頭。當時陪伴史特福特的不止是隊友，還有一隻聖班納犬叫Major。<br />\n<br />\n雖然史特福特很努力籌錢，但最後錢都是不夠，最令人傷心的是，被視為球隊吉祥物的Major在籌款期間，走失了。以為是屋漏偏逢連夜雨，但原來是柳暗花明又一村，Major成為扭轉形勢的關鍵。史特福特找不到Major，但有個好心人叫戴維斯（John Henry Davies）找到，2人相約見面。戴維斯是一間啤酒廠東主，當時他正想找隻狗送給女兒做生日禮物，他對Major一見鍾情，所以想向史特福特買Major。<br />\n<br />\n史特福特及戴維斯在啤酒廠見面，史特福特同意將Major給戴維斯，而條件是戴維斯要拯救Newton Heath。在1902年，戴維斯與另外3名曼市商人合資，以白武士身份注資Newton Heath，為球會還清債務。戴維斯控制球會後，先後有兩項革命性改變，首先將球隊主色由綠色及金色，變成紅色及白色，並將球隊名稱由Newton Heath改為Manchester United。因此，沒有Major的話，曼聯不會是今日的曼聯，牠是曼聯史上最關鍵的曼狗。"},{"pid":"5ae73af1c9933f54ba5e4cb1562113bb4ba847e9","tid":643887,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"100年後有摩狗幫手fing哂啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180755954c02000d85051bfd79c49dd21d1ab5f3","tid":643887,"uid":99856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae73af1c9933f54ba5e4cb1562113bb4ba847e9","tid":643887,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:38:23.000Z","msg":"100年後有摩狗幫手fing哂啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0174749660575fcb0399c2778effbea4c578f827","tid":643887,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:44:40.000Z","msg":"49000"},{"pid":"40882aedb1d69600667f39430b24f186916f2e8d","tid":643887,"uid":42034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"屌柒你地班死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38cf02e7a7aae53dced7f30cff5467b4cbca2495","tid":643887,"uid":42246,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"為左隊波 賣左自己隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獌狗果然係獌狗 冇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec7947e5428aac19af4c1744c465aca4ed21bb3","tid":643887,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38cf02e7a7aae53dced7f30cff5467b4cbca2495","tid":643887,"uid":42246,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"為左隊波 賣左自己隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n獌狗果然係獌狗 冇性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" c